    <item>
      <title>麦克莱姆对通胀回到目标感到高兴，希望进一步实施核心宽松政策</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/macklem-pleased-inflation-back-to-target-wants-more-core-easing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大央行行长蒂芙·麦克勒姆表示，他很高兴通胀率回到央行 2% 的目标，但他希望看到核心指标和住房价格进一步放松。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-24/macklem-pleased-inflation-back-to-target-wants-more-core-easing</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 24 Sep 2024 16:55:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
